### Example: AWS SSH over Session Manager
# https://docs.aws.amazon.com/systems-manager/latest/userguide/session-manager-getting-started-enable-ssh-connections.html
# Host example-aws-host
#     HostName     lolkekaws
#     User         lolkekowicz
#     ProxyCommand sh -c "aws ssm start-session --target %h --document-name AWS-StartSSHSession --parameters 'portNumber=%p' --region lolkek --profile profile-xxx"
